Text: RE NDAEDF Mann International Inc Cc getting back now and will pass along to legal and chase up Original Message From mailto Sent Monday October PM To Cc Subject NDAEDF Mann International Inc Mary At the request of Bob Shults I am attaching our proposed form of NonDisclosure Agreement Please call me or Bob with any comments or questions you might have My phone no is and Bob can be reached at If the agreement meets with your approval please fax a signed copy to me at We look forward to hearing from you See attached file edf manndoc
